quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  39,64,Boola “owulali Nyasaye niye wamunomesinjia okhulaama enywe Abasilu?”
  39,65,"Ne toto wafimbulilwa nende balia abaliho imbeli wuwo mbu : “notsokaasia Nyasaye ebikhole bibio bioosi bilakwa akhaya, ne toto oliba Mubandu basikha.”"
  39,66,Halali laama butswa Nyasaye mana obe mubalia bakhupanga orio
  39,67,"Ne shibamuwa Nyasaye oluyali shingala kenyekhana tawe, ne eshialo shiosi shiliba mumukhono kukwe, ne likulu lilikanyakanywa liaba mumukhono kukwe omulunji, oluyali ni olulwe Owekulu nomutwenufu khukabamutsokaasinjia ninako"
  39,68,"Ne olwika lulikhupwa mana bifwe bioosi ebili mwikulu nende khushialo halali ulia wa Nyasaye alichama, mana khandi lulikhupwa olundi mana boosi balibukha nibahenga"
  39,69,"Mana eshialo shiliakha khubulafu bwa Nyasaye washio Omulesi, ne eshitabu shilirerwa, ne Abarumwa balirerwa nende Abaloli, mana barungwe omurungo kwa toto nabo shibalikholelwa obubii tawe"
  39,70,"Mana buli shiamundu alirungwa kayakholanga , naye (Nyasaye) yamanya muno kabakholanga"